{"tid":1445982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀爆眼，老銅狗臥底，葵芳站內催淚彈，北角警黑","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:37:16.000Z","uid":131125,"like":145,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"fd41ba04352ce26e266429df59c8b499f0a50255","tid":1445982,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">人道問題：射爆果位女士眼珠同埋站內放催淚毒氣要向外國宣傳，更大力度爭取人道組織同外國關注</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">老銅臥底就要向深藍同淺藍宣傳<br />\n務求要令佢地相信至今為止絕大部份衝擊同武力行為都係狗一手做起，<strong>佢地一直鬧緊嘅都係狗臥底</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">北角警黑向中間同淺黃<br />\n令佢地知道福建佬打人警狗坐視不理<br />\n喺正隔離都放犯唔捉，<strong>呢個地方唔再安全</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最緊要最緊要<br />\n唔好俾某一邊cover哂其他野<br />\n全部都推爆佢<br />\n功利啲講，都發生左就要盡力利用好佢</span></strong><br />\n留個方向俾所有文宣手足煲大佢"},{"pid":"c743b36767a5d37f1ee6e01ec24dab4dbbe77876","tid":1445982,"uid":131125,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"好撚心痛<br />\n但唔利用哂佢手足就傷得無價值"},{"pid":"7a8c661906421d2ae8cacb7cf2fa95eb8bf357bd","tid":1445982,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5054ba7225b527cd86904c9481868789c107a87f","tid":1445982,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"推，屌"},{"pid":"ec6b8551e522cb7627d191c1d908ee97fb7a281f","tid":1445982,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea0d0a47fc9e96ae48f2b14dc6ff9572454cf597","tid":1445982,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"推佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死黑警"},{"pid":"3ac29aaf4eedaf63dcab8946daee7c488ff59bb3","tid":1445982,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201